message.text:
𝐊𝐀𝐒𝐘𝐀 𝐏𝐀 𝐋𝐈𝐌𝐀! 𝐀𝐑𝐓𝐈𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐌𝐒, 𝐒𝐀𝐊𝐀𝐘 𝐍𝐀 𝐒𝐀 𝐋𝐎𝐀𝐃𝐒!

This is our last day of applying to the League of Arts and Design so don’t miss the chance to join! For interested applicants, you can fill out the necessary details on the provided form:
https://forms.gle/1Wd7kX1eS7DAQUtx7

‼️Please note that this form will only be open until 11:59‼️

You can refer to this link to learn more about the different committees and see what fits for you! 
https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1Fr79h28yk/?mibextid=wwXIfr

For any inquiries or concerns, do not hesitate to contact us by messaging our official Facebook page or via email: loads@feu.edu.ph

#FEULOADS #LoadStarforLoneStars

Publication Material by
Gianna Vega
Caption by 
Brian Cachin

message.text:
CHARGE, TAMARAWS, CHARGE TO LUNETA! ✊️

[NEW ASSEMBLY POINT]

Ika nga ni Nicanor Reyes Sr., "BE BRAVE!" 💚

Iniimbitahan ng League of Filipino Students FEU ang lahat ng Tamaraws na makiisa sa mga gaganaping programa sa Setyembre 19 at Setyembre 21 para sa paniningil sa talamak na korapsyon at kawalang pananagutan mula kina Marcos-Duterte hanggang sa mga kakampi nito sa gobyerno. 🔥

Bukas, Setyembre 19, ay may gaganaping Black Friday Protest: 
4:00 pm - Assembly @ P. Noval
5:00 pm - March to FEU Gate 4, then Program

Sa Setyembre 21 naman, narito ang programa: 
8:00 am - Assembly of One Ubelt @ Kartilya ng Katipunan
9:00 am - March to Luneta 

I-scan lang ang QR code sa picture upang makasali! 

#MarcosSingilinDutertePanagutin
#NotoCorruption
#Luneta
